{"tid":1170554,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[低質小眾] 物理研究小遊戲","createTime":"2019-05-25T05:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T12:32:59.000Z","uid":147721,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"439dd692e48b8da2a93029663431b9b3dde5d13c","tid":1170554,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T05:30:04.000Z","msg":"開波之前講4點<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔好quote長文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 呢個小遊戲非常非常小眾 唔係㩒兩下個啲flash game 比標題呃左既可以負評上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心好小眾 我都預左無人會同我玩<br />\n其實我係舊登試過玩類似既野 不過零回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果無人玩既 我就會死心 唔再用同類野浪費網絡資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 由於我要返工 所以之後都只係會有心情有時間先會出po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且topic係跟我心情 唔一定好連貫 大家唔好對後續有期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 要用電腦開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555a2b650dc0eb204ddcb7bc4fc00a72e3e2868e","tid":1170554,"uid":147721,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"大家想唔想知物理研究係點既一回事呢<br />\n每個科學家都有佢既研究風格 無絕對既<br />\n呢個po就用一個toy model黎體驗下 其中一個風格<br />\n<a href=\"https://embed.plnkr.co/jsMi5oltGnT0Jn38js3v?autoCloseSidebar=true&amp;show=demo-opt.c,preview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fembed.plnkr.co%2FjsMi5oltGnT0Jn38js3v%3FautoCloseSidebar%3Dtrue%26show%3Ddemo-opt.c%2Cpreview&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62ILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=ea287687\" target=\"_blank\">https://embed.plnkr.co/jsMi5oltGnT0Jn38js3v?autoCloseSidebar=true&amp;show=demo-opt.c,preview</a><br />\n呢個係一個particle collision既模擬器<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地既遊戲玩法 就係<br />\n1. 觀察呢個model有咩現象<br />\n2. 將你既觀察同推論寫上黎<br />\n如果比人圍屌 就係輸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n贏既獎品 就係對個model有更深既認識 同埋可以自high<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我首先拋磚問幾條課題<br />\n1. 粒子既分佈係點 有咩驅使佢地咁分佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 大型粒子之間 傾向痴埋一齊 定係分開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 頭十五秒 粒子既運動係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解會咁運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554f922419c32316b2f827f5be2e6fcad69ded4c","tid":1170554,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:08:51.000Z","msg":"留名睇野"},{"pid":"154cf3811308800582f420cfb215da503537fe0d","tid":1170554,"uid":11311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:35:58.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"cbea635ed43123610f3520c321cd626e5f9d5842","tid":1170554,"uid":193294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:55:36.000Z","msg":"留名玩野"},{"pid":"ef6ebbb1cc79aa73d8d457e5ad7064114e32133c","tid":1170554,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:56:59.000Z","msg":"留名出野"},{"pid":"5a971cc03c1d862e43da77fffdc366fa6c61188f","tid":1170554,"uid":136590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"Wiener process??<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fed6f0849f13f8f75839ef3d44e135aeeda40de","tid":1170554,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:50:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04d1572c7a7f454a101156f1a82a2594f7c1fe98","tid":1170554,"uid":4526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:52:32.000Z","msg":"1.<br />\n上面粒子大啲，下面粒子密度高啲<br />\n<br />\n因爲大粒子表面面積大，容易俾粒子撞。而因爲下面粒子密度高啲，所以俾下面嘅粒子撞嘅機會俾上面粒子撞嘅機會大。所以大粒子會浮。<br />\n<br />\n因爲重力同俾大粒子壓住，所以下面粒子密度高啲<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n唔識睇<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n粒子向下跌，然後散開<br />\n<br />\ngravity同diffusion？"},{"pid":"d03c43176af69a15533118aa1d4ff0261d24ade0","tid":1170554,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04d1572c7a7f454a101156f1a82a2594f7c1fe98","tid":1170554,"uid":4526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:52:32.000Z","msg":"1.<br />\n上面粒子大啲，下面粒子密度高啲<br />\n<br />\n因爲大粒子表面面積大，容易俾粒子撞。而因爲下面粒子密度高啲，所以俾下面嘅粒子撞嘅機會俾上面粒子撞嘅機會大。所以大粒子會浮。<br />\n<br />\n因爲重力同俾大粒子壓住，所以下面粒子密度高啲<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n唔識睇<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n粒子向下跌，然後散開<br />\n<br />\ngravity同diffusion？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有人玩<br />\n<br />\n1. 咁大粒子既平衡位置係點決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇式<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 咁試下諗呢句陳述啱定錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「兩粒大粒子拍埋一齊個時 因為佢地之間無細粒子提供壓力 所以佢地會因外部壓力而痴埋一齊」<br />\n<br />\n3. 所有粒子跌到最低之後 大粒子既運動係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302b4d673a7a2e53e5ff84ed61c56add9d5c6c0e","tid":1170554,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:06:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45c735f4ae36e27060e3b47338ab8d8d49921441","tid":1170554,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:15:56.000Z","msg":"依個模型體現左量子力學入面天人合一果種上帝半死不活既西班牙現象邏輯學理論既創新觀點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鳩up only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依個post幾得意 返屋企再睇"},{"pid":"5bcbab7251308541874ebac99cbfa7bdda6ec3ef","tid":1170554,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d03c43176af69a15533118aa1d4ff0261d24ade0","tid":1170554,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04d1572c7a7f454a101156f1a82a2594f7c1fe98","tid":1170554,"uid":4526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:52:32.000Z","msg":"1.<br />\n上面粒子大啲，下面粒子密度高啲<br />\n<br />\n因爲大粒子表面面積大，容易俾粒子撞。而因爲下面粒子密度高啲，所以俾下面嘅粒子撞嘅機會俾上面粒子撞嘅機會大。所以大粒子會浮。<br />\n<br />\n因爲重力同俾大粒子壓住，所以下面粒子密度高啲<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n唔識睇<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n粒子向下跌，然後散開<br />\n<br />\ngravity同diffusion？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有人玩<br />\n<br />\n1. 咁大粒子既平衡位置係點決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇式<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 咁試下諗呢句陳述啱定錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「兩粒大粒子拍埋一齊個時 因為佢地之間無細粒子提供壓力 所以佢地會因外部壓力而痴埋一齊」<br />\n<br />\n3. 所有粒子跌到最低之後 大粒子既運動係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T12:58:35.000Z","msg":"1.<br />\nAt equilibrium vertical position 大粒子嘅vertical velocity, v_y = 0<br />\n同 d(v_y)/dt = 0<br />\n<br />\n如果at equilibrium某個時間點有n粒粒子撞落大粒子i度 咁大粒子i嘅d(v_y)/dt:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EpmUc1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEpmUc1B.gif&h=94b4627a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFrom observation, frequency of collision應該係dependent on y position<br />\n即係條式個summation係y dependent<br />\n咁如果有個y coordinate係同時符合v_y = 0 同 條式 咁果個y就係大粒子i嘅equilibrium y coordinate<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n好似無錯 不過有時啲細粒子會頂開啲大粒子sip入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n當所有粒子跌到最底 因爲下面嘅粒子好多而上面嘅粒子好少<br />\n所以底嘅粒子會將面嘅粒子向上推<br />\n因爲大粒子嘅面積大 被撞擊嘅機會較高 所以大粒子會畀其他粒子彈上頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d136b7ef1b7ad54ab996680854ecc922ecb5394f","tid":1170554,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T13:10:54.000Z","msg":"3.<br />\n大粒子會keep住係頂一陣 然後會慢慢跌去equilibrium position"},{"pid":"b8d653b97ffe52193dfb0d5c8e408a21dd42f567","tid":1170554,"uid":86196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d03c43176af69a15533118aa1d4ff0261d24ade0","tid":1170554,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04d1572c7a7f454a101156f1a82a2594f7c1fe98","tid":1170554,"uid":4526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:52:32.000Z","msg":"1.<br />\n上面粒子大啲，下面粒子密度高啲<br />\n<br />\n因爲大粒子表面面積大，容易俾粒子撞。而因爲下面粒子密度高啲，所以俾下面嘅粒子撞嘅機會俾上面粒子撞嘅機會大。所以大粒子會浮。<br />\n<br />\n因爲重力同俾大粒子壓住，所以下面粒子密度高啲<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n唔識睇<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n粒子向下跌，然後散開<br />\n<br />\ngravity同diffusion？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有人玩<br />\n<br />\n1. 咁大粒子既平衡位置係點決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇式<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 咁試下諗呢句陳述啱定錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「兩粒大粒子拍埋一齊個時 因為佢地之間無細粒子提供壓力 所以佢地會因外部壓力而痴埋一齊」<br />\n<br />\n3. 所有粒子跌到最低之後 大粒子既運動係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:32:59.000Z","msg":"手巴識埋diffusion<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset